{"comments":"Progress Atom — Normalized animation progress value [0.0, 1.0].\n\nProgress represents the current state of an animation or process:\n- 0.0: Start\n- 1.0: End\n\nValues are clamped to [0.0, 1.0] to ensure valid interpolation.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","Progress"],"Progress"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[54,42],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Progress.purs","start":[54,1]},"title":"eqProgress"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","Progress"],"Progress"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[55,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Progress.purs","start":[55,1]},"title":"ordProgress"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","Progress"],"Progress"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[58,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Progress.purs","start":[57,1]},"title":"showProgress"}],"comments":"Normalized progress value [0.0, 1.0]\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[52,35],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Progress.purs","start":[52,1]},"title":"Progress"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create Progress, clamping to [0.0, 1.0].\n\nNaN and Infinity are clamped to 0.0 (start of progress).\nFor explicit rejection of invalid values, use `safeProgress`.\n\n```purescript\nprogress 0.5         -- Progress 0.5\nprogress 1.5         -- Progress 1.0 (clamped)\nprogress (-0.5)      -- Progress 0.0 (clamped)\nprogress (0.0 / 0.0) -- Progress 0.0 (NaN clamped)\nprogress (1.0 / 0.0) -- Progress 0.0 (Infinity clamped)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","Progress"],"Progress"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[72,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Progress.purs","start":[72,1]},"title":"progress"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create Progress with explicit validation, rejecting invalid values.\n\nReturns Nothing for NaN, Infinity, or values outside [0.0, 1.0].\nThis is the **secure** constructor — use it at system boundaries.\n\n```purescript\nsafeProgress 0.5         -- Just (Progress 0.5)\nsafeProgress 1.5         -- Nothing (exceeds 1.0)\nsafeProgress (-0.5)      -- Nothing (negative)\nsafeProgress (0.0 / 0.0) -- Nothing (NaN rejected)\nsafeProgress (1.0 / 0.0) -- Nothing (Infinity rejected)\n```\n\n## Security Model\n\nNaN and Infinity are attack vectors. A malicious actor crafting\n`0.0 / 0.0` or `1.0 / 0.0` can bypass naive bounds checks.\nThis function explicitly rejects these values at the boundary.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Maybe"],"Maybe"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","Progress"],"Progress"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[97,41],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Progress.purs","start":[97,1]},"title":"safeProgress"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create Progress without bounds checking\n\nUse only when you have already validated the value is in [0.0, 1.0].\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","Progress"],"Progress"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[107,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Progress.purs","start":[107,1]},"title":"unsafeProgress"},{"children":[],"comments":"Extract raw Number from Progress\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","Progress"],"Progress"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[111,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Temporal/Progress.purs","start":[111,1]},"title":"unwrapProgress"},{"children":[],"comments":"Alias for unwrapProgress\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Temporal","Progress"],"Progress"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[1